  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A buffet breakfast is prepared for you each morning where you'll find a great selection including <span>pastries, brioches and local Garda honey. </span></p>
<p><strong>Restaurant Il Philo</strong> is the hotel's <span>à la carte</span> restaurant. It's open for lunch and dinner and offers local cuisine using fresh produce. The summer menu is comprised of antipasto, primo and secondo courses, as well as deserts. Guests are entitled to a 10% discount here. The restaurant is closed on a Monday.</p>
<p>A Gourmet Dinner Package is pre-bookable for a supplement of 97 euros. It includes a three-course dinner at the <em>Restaurant</em> <em>Il Philo</em> for three nights during your stay. </p>
<p><strong>The Art Deco Bar</strong> offers a spot of opulence which spills out onto the stunning garden terrace where lanterns, fire pits and fairy lights await you. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
