  <description><![CDATA[<p>You’ll find Hotel Park in <a data-udi="umb://document/574a76e62f8b4388af2fd61b34c7ed1b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/574a76e62f8b4388af2fd61b34c7ed1b}" title="Desenzano">Desenzano's</a> centre. The town’s many amenities are on your doorstep and the lake is directly in front of the hotel. Desezano’s popular public beach is just 150 metres away. The hotel’s façade is beautifully historic and the interiors are stylish and modern. It’s been finished in warm colours and feels very comfortable and homely. Every room is spacious and floor-to-ceiling windows let in plenty of light. Private balconies look out over the town or <a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">Lake Garda</a>.</p>
<p>Head to the roof for the spectacular pool with panoramic lake views. Grab a sun lounger and relax here all day – the bar service will keep you refreshed with cocktails and aperitivi. If you’re after a quieter spot, head for the decked terrace. Comfy sofas are set amongst various plants and there are plenty of shady spots too.</p>
<p>The <span>à la carte</span> restaurant, Il Philo, has a great choice of Italian dishes. Upgrade to the Gourmet Dinner Package and you'll dine here for three nights during your stay. Make sure you spend some time in the bar afterwards. It’s perfect for a night cap.</p>
<p>Transfer time: approx. 45 mins by coach from Verona airport.</p>]]></description>
