  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Park is a modern hotel in Desenzano's historic centre. The lake is right on the doorstep and you'll get incredible lake views from the rooftop pool. If that wasn't enough, it also has incredible food, wonderful service and a beautiful lakeside terrace that'll be hard to take yourself away from.</p>]]></listingDescription>
