  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Elegance Rooms </strong>are spacious with a modern design. They measure 25m² and have a balcony with town or garden views, a double bed, air conditioning, TV, safe, minibar, hairdryer and shower. Bathrobes are available on request.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms</strong> are about 22m² and sleep two people. They have lake views from the balcony and a double or twin beds with a bath or shower.</p>
<p><strong>Prestige Junior Suites</strong> are approximately 38m² and can sleep up to four people. The extra bed is a double sofa bed. They have a separate seating area and a balcony. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
